  "detailed_description": "NBB Arena is the sport of tomorrow. Generations of robots have dreamt of becoming the next NBB superstar.<br><br>Every cycle, NEON Corp holds a Qualifier to welcome new, promising Bombers, challenging them with increasingly deadly gauntlets that test even the most skilled competitors.<br><br>Only the best survive.<br><br><strong>Now it's your turn.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/76fdc98b0599bc56e5b824e51d826302.webp?t=1736004931\" width=616 height=42 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/9bf531b2d892e7aab611cd3e20bf0fcb.poster.avif?t=1736004931\" width=720 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/9bf531b2d892e7aab611cd3e20bf0fcb.webm?t=1736004931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/9bf531b2d892e7aab611cd3e20bf0fcb.mp4?t=1736004931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/601079b066955d31d869476a05020629.webp?t=1736004931\" width=616 height=42 /></span><br><br>New bombers are encouraged to:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Complete challenging sequences to improve their motor skills.<br></li><li> Solve difficult puzzles and demonstrate their logical processing ability.<br></li><li> Traverse various namespaces across The System.<br></li><li> Face off against menacing Master Programs.<br></li><li> Engage with up to 3 other local bombers in cooperative progression or through competitive matches. <br></li><li> Decode the <strong>[REDACTED][REDACTED][REDACTED]</strong> of the <strong>[REDACTED]</strong>.</li></ul><br><strong>IMPORTANT </strong>: CONTROLLERS ARE REQUIRED FOR LOCAL MULTIPLAYER.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/551fc98d2ff6ffdd6e645f357ecb6b5b.avif?t=1736004931\" width=616 height=154 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/32a68353c0df7cf0e6e0dd8395318278.webp?t=1736004931\" width=616 height=42 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/01a410480c409a12e326afcc16055bb1.poster.avif?t=1736004931\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/01a410480c409a12e326afcc16055bb1.webm?t=1736004931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/01a410480c409a12e326afcc16055bb1.mp4?t=1736004931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/77f172c05f4fa4c689de997e39081164.webp?t=1736004931\" width=616 height=42 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/1ae775e86adc30ee4d058a142f6dd695.poster.avif?t=1736004931\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/1ae775e86adc30ee4d058a142f6dd695.webm?t=1736004931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845720/extras/1ae775e86adc30ee4d058a142f6dd695.mp4?t=1736004931